Darrow - #67 With the song coming to an end, Ness manages to snap out of his funk. Unfortunately for him, he missed out on the chance to make an easy $50.
Darrow - #68 Without the Pencil Eraser, Ness finds himself trapped. Unfortunately for him, game mechanics prevent him from going forward. Poor Ness...if only he knew this was a comic based on a game.

Darrow - #69 Apple Kid is dead! ...Well, not really. Ness gets his hands on a powerful creation. Also, Apple Kid is set to star in his own game as the villain who wishes to eradicate all art from the world. Such evil.
Darrow - #07 Pokey and King join the party! Ness face palms, and we discover Pokey's deep-seated fear of Dracula.
